{"tid":370080,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪usj一問","createTime":"2017-08-22T21:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T02:08:16.000Z","uid":84757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd162fc0a432bf1f07dae6fbe1aeb19d9872c92","tid":370080,"uid":84757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:26:52.000Z","msg":"下個月會去usj 考慮緊買唔買快證<br />\n<br />\n因為我睇預計人數唔多 始終都暑假完<br />\n<br />\n我咁諗啱唔啱<br />\n<br />\n定暑假完都會好多人<br />\n<br />\n未去過唔係好知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acc3aaf76731c3482bb35d5147e387216dfee5e","tid":370080,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:29:22.000Z","msg":"買翼龍果個快證已經夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申買左"},{"pid":"5c0c857cba104bbbbd458c25dca7afd929ef2151","tid":370080,"uid":90128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:08:47.000Z","msg":"真心睇運 上次平日去排一個鐘一個game <br />\n朋友都係平日去 15分鐘至半個鐘就玩到<br />\n利申 我同朋友係6月頭去"},{"pid":"299f46693b7bfd47b19e4cbc9bb63c2895482210","tid":370080,"uid":20971,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:10:41.000Z","msg":"上連登問多數都叫你買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa2d90f1001adcdad08af026f4d8743cb2d446e9","tid":370080,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:20:21.000Z","msg":"買FP千祈唔好揀terminator<br />\n一定要買翼龍個隻"},{"pid":"6745ac896892f4d54076cbf82174af74560c6853","tid":370080,"uid":71209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:48:45.000Z","msg":"上年暑假完 平日去 買左快證翼龍排左兩個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cc9a3874cb6045a0312227196fd1d3801d3ef6","tid":370080,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T01:49:36.000Z","msg":"唔買, 早D去排必玩果D<br />\n其他玩唔到就算"},{"pid":"f6fd0c9bbaf0d3167212a5a508ac8a7ab11d28be","tid":370080,"uid":56803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"無買express <br />\nNo VIP<br />\n830準時入場 去harry potter <br />\n等左30分鐘玩得<br />\n全日玩左<br />\n翼龍,dinosaur trip,Harry Potter, 鷹馬的飛行<br />\n逆轉世紀, fantasy space, spider man,<br />\nTerminator, 大白鯊<br />\n只有鷹馬飛行過60分鐘 因為中途15分鐘壞車<br />\n其他30分鐘左右<br />\n排single."},{"pid":"2dbc351a38c8c68ec19453ed60cbeec93edbe3a9","tid":370080,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:48:34.000Z","msg":"買<br />\n暑假一個game排2個鐘以上<br />\n利申usj做pt"},{"pid":"2ab33556ddff6f47d79df33cd09201268f2ee81c","tid":370080,"uid":135118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"翼龍4"},{"pid":"dae90e8b5b92c1c83a67252508238e05c4bbd216","tid":370080,"uid":17166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"如果樓主係一個獨撚自己去 就唔使買快證 反正可以排single ride，或者無人care你玩左幾多遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果樓主係同囡囡一齊去 就死都一定要買，因為唔使俾人詐型，又可以用更多時間囡囡玩更多嘅嘢，囡囡嬲人係唔使講理由，何況而家有充分嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早上玩得開心，晚上先至玩得更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a4a875686a84d0d95b7cd30100c282916d77c6","tid":370080,"uid":17166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"利申: 7月份去完，買左逆向7<br />\n<br />\n我首先9衝入去玩翼龍，唔使點排隊，玩完仲可以encore玩多次， 先至夠鐘玩FP的第一個遊戲<br />\n<br />\n全日玩左13個遊戲，睇住人哋排隊，自已直行直過好開心，用錢係買唔到呢種暗爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同意樓上所講，Terminator 真係一個好on9嘅遊戲， 完全浪費時間。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我之前都玩過大白鯊，on9指數其實差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算係豬頭骨的一個game"},{"pid":"96e5ffa757b7d0b3b8bbd4b62d01954c58fa8960","tid":370080,"uid":56803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果樓主係一個獨撚自己去 就唔使買快證 反正可以排single ride，或者無人care你玩左幾多遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果樓主係同囡囡一齊去 就死都一定要買，因為唔使俾人詐型，又可以用更多時間囡囡玩更多嘅嘢，囡囡嬲人係唔使講理由，何況而家有充分嘅理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早上玩得開心，晚上先至玩得更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同女去先要買, 男人可以一齊排single, 只係分開坐"},{"pid":"d05ddb8de3d28c8c68c45b43b9f99b4acb7cad3d","tid":370080,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"買啦<br />\n安全D"},{"pid":"7a19c4b5af0c663140eef3b2d3f9bb0101d571cf","tid":370080,"uid":128550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"有冇人知電子飛可唔可以加錢換番實體飛"},{"pid":"cad3499628ca61885fe8a2dd6ac96f28297e7519","tid":370080,"uid":128550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}